==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Descendant
<hw>De*scend"ant</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who descends, as
offspring, however remotely; -- correlative to <xex>ancestor</xex> or
<xex>ascendant</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Our first parents and their <qex>descendants</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Hale.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>descendant</qex> of so many kings and emperors.</q>
<rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>descendants</ent>⟦br⟧
